author: Tyler Olson
title: House Dems call for release of 'as many prisoners as possible' due to coronavirus pandemic
description: Democrats on the House Judiciary Committee sent a letter Monday to Attorney General Bill Barr asking him to "release as many prisoners as possible" as federal prisons work to deal with uniquely difficult circumstances during the coronavirus pandemic.
